Items.mt: The willow crows are always in the daytime, and the pond is filled with wind and flutter in the autumn garden. In the 36 palaces, the hairpins are decorated with bright powder and thick fragrance. The first of these is the "King of Flowers". The night is bright with thousands of candles. The years of light are kept in the shadow.
